02:06.293 --> 02:09.751
September 4, 1980
palermo, Saint rosalia's day

02:11.131 --> 02:14.043
cosa nostra bosses meet
at Stefano bontade's villa.

02:14.301 --> 02:16.508
Palermo is the world capital of heroin.

02:16.678 --> 02:19.670
The old palermo mafia
and the new corleone clan

02:19.890 --> 02:22.552
meet to divvy up the heroin trade,

02:22.768 --> 02:24.679
thus avoiding another mafia war.

02:32.819 --> 02:35.499
The fugitive tommaso buscetta,"boss
of two worlds", is also present.

02:35.697 --> 02:38.188
As a simple "soldier", he can not
participate in the meeting,

02:38.450 --> 02:40.970
but he has influence with bontade,
head of the palermo alliance.

02:43.914 --> 02:46.030
Buscetta attends
with his third wife Christina

02:46.208 --> 02:48.164
and children from his previous marriages.

03:34.256 --> 03:36.588
Where are you going? Papal!

04:13.670 --> 04:15.877
- Papa...
- C'mon, get up!

04:17.798 --> 04:19.005
Get up!

04:19.426 --> 04:22.132
- Papa, why are you hitting me?
- Benedetto, let's go.

04:22.804 --> 04:24.920
Papa, I love you.

04:30.187 --> 04:31.643
God is love.

04:35.692 --> 04:37.307
Gimme a hug, papa.

04:44.326 --> 04:46.408
A toast to our friends.

04:50.081 --> 04:52.163
And to our families.

04:53.210 --> 04:55.201
And to money!

04:56.046 --> 04:57.707
Cheers!

05:04.846 --> 05:06.928
Here, take your brother!

05:19.986 --> 05:21.851
Come, let's dance
to something lively!

05:21.988 --> 05:24.479
Let's dance! Music, maestro!

05:36.378 --> 05:37.709
What's wrong?

05:44.135 --> 05:46.342
Your wife's good, isn't she?

05:46.847 --> 05:50.135
She raised all these kids
without having kids and stepkids.

05:52.853 --> 05:55.014
Masino, will you tell me
what's wrong?

05:55.772 --> 05:57.262
Do you see benedetto?

05:58.024 --> 05:59.889
He looks done in.

06:02.237 --> 06:04.102
Yeah, done in...

06:05.740 --> 06:08.152
- How did it end up?
- All good.

06:28.680 --> 06:31.171
Why don't you have them come with us?

06:31.308 --> 06:34.175
They don't want to,
this is their life.

06:34.436 --> 06:38.645
- You have to force them.
- They're not kids anymore.

06:38.815 --> 06:42.774
Antonio's made me a grandfather.
Stop talking nonsense.

06:43.069 --> 06:44.309
You don't want them.

06:44.571 --> 06:48.189
Yeah, I don't want them in Brazil.
They're lost.

07:39.250 --> 07:40.990
A photo!

07:41.127 --> 07:42.742
A nice photo!

07:43.964 --> 07:45.704
This will be fun!

07:50.637 --> 07:53.720
- Hide that gun.
- Why, can you see it?

07:54.975 --> 07:56.761
Masino, come here!

07:57.477 --> 07:59.092
Toto, you come here too.

07:59.854 --> 08:01.469
Everyone's gotta be in it.

08:01.648 --> 08:03.639
The kids too, here.

08:03.900 --> 08:07.859
For this beautiful family and for
this peace that must never end.

08:14.911 --> 08:16.242
Peace?

08:16.538 --> 08:17.778
A farse...

08:25.422 --> 08:26.912
Be careful.

08:27.298 --> 08:29.414
The first to start, never loses.

08:55.035 --> 08:58.573
Long live Saint rosalia!

09:15.346 --> 09:19.089
The infirm want your grace.

09:19.184 --> 09:22.051
Long live Saint rosalia!

09:22.479 --> 09:25.937
Step by step we'll bring you.

09:25.982 --> 09:28.564
Long live Saint rosalia!

09:28.735 --> 09:31.351
In every street on every road.

09:31.446 --> 09:34.609
Long live Saint rosalia!

09:35.617 --> 09:38.984
He who does not say it with me
is not a devotee.

09:39.496 --> 09:41.862
Long live Saint rosalia!

09:42.373 --> 09:46.457
Thunder and storms and we call you.

09:53.009 --> 09:54.624
I'm leaving.

09:55.220 --> 09:56.585
When?

09:57.597 --> 09:59.713
Why are you leaving now?

10:00.141 --> 10:03.850
Things are getting better,
can't you see all the money circulating?

10:04.020 --> 10:06.477
You can't take money
to the grave with you.

10:06.898 --> 10:09.105
You have to look after
benedetto and Antonio.

10:09.150 --> 10:11.015
You know they're like sons to me.

10:37.137 --> 10:40.174
The traitor

10:53.069 --> 10:56.937
December 1980,
Rio de Janeiro, grumari beach

10:59.450 --> 11:01.441
be careful, it's dangerous!

11:15.216 --> 11:17.457
The water's dangerous.

11:21.347 --> 11:23.053
You're freezing.

11:23.099 --> 11:24.964
I couldn't get out of the water.

12:58.194 --> 13:01.436
Remember, father, your church
spread all over the earth,

13:01.698 --> 13:05.282
make it perfect in love and in the
union with our pope John Paul...

13:24.095 --> 13:27.212
Stefano, I baptize you
in the name of the father,

13:27.307 --> 13:30.094
the son and the holy spirit.

13:32.353 --> 13:33.684
Thank you.

13:41.112 --> 13:43.103
Long live Stefano!

13:48.494 --> 13:50.450
We have a problem with the stopover.

13:50.830 --> 13:53.617
When the undersecretary realized
it was for planes

13:53.875 --> 13:56.366
arriving from Peru,
Bolivia and Colombia...

13:58.087 --> 14:00.248
Two plus two equals four.

14:03.343 --> 14:06.255
- How much did he ask you for?
- One and a half.

14:06.846 --> 14:09.007
Let's make it two... three.

14:09.265 --> 14:10.755
All right.

14:11.142 --> 14:13.758
I'd like to go live there
with all my family.

14:14.896 --> 14:16.011
In amazonia?

14:16.898 --> 14:19.605
- You want to be a hermit?
- Let's go.

14:22.111 --> 14:23.396
Your excellency.

14:23.654 --> 14:26.896
Mr felici!
What a lovely family you have!

14:26.991 --> 14:28.902
Thank you very much. Madam.

14:30.370 --> 14:34.534
Yes, the truth is I'm happy here
with my family, my father-in-law...

14:34.791 --> 14:36.372
We're among friends

14:37.293 --> 14:40.501
and when you're among friends
you can get around any problem.

14:41.798 --> 14:43.379
Gentlemen, please.

14:46.052 --> 14:47.167
Hold it.

14:48.054 --> 14:49.510
One more.

14:56.020 --> 14:58.011
What's he doing here?

15:04.821 --> 15:06.402
Here we go...

15:16.707 --> 15:18.197
Don't be afraid, pippo.

15:19.794 --> 15:21.330
Stay down!

15:58.583 --> 16:00.494
You gotta be quiet.

16:11.471 --> 16:13.507
Out!

16:13.639 --> 16:17.097
- It was out!
- Masino, it was in!

16:17.351 --> 16:19.592
No, it was out.

16:21.355 --> 16:24.142
Mr felici, a personal call for you.

16:25.651 --> 16:27.141
It's over.

16:27.361 --> 16:29.647
Drinks for everyone, on me.

16:30.156 --> 16:32.112
That was a goal!

16:35.912 --> 16:37.027
Hello?

16:37.413 --> 16:38.744
How are you?

16:41.167 --> 16:42.282
Who's this?

16:42.668 --> 16:44.283
Don't you recognize me?

16:44.795 --> 16:46.626
A friend, masino.

16:47.173 --> 16:48.504
How are you?

16:49.300 --> 16:51.165
The family all good?

17:30.216 --> 17:33.549
- What'd you say at your pa's funeral?
- What did I say?

17:35.096 --> 17:37.462
You said you want to avenge him.

17:37.682 --> 17:39.172
Yeah, it's true.

17:39.725 --> 17:42.432
Whoever killed him's gonna
meet the same end!

17:43.604 --> 17:45.686
Have you ever fired a gun?

17:46.357 --> 17:47.357
Yes.

17:48.442 --> 17:50.603
With the right or with the left?

17:51.237 --> 17:52.977
I don't understand.

18:19.515 --> 18:20.880
Everything okay?

18:26.022 --> 18:27.387
Everything good?

18:27.773 --> 18:29.513
All quiet, sir.

18:56.552 --> 18:58.417
Papa!

19:18.324 --> 19:19.689
Sit down.

19:27.166 --> 19:30.909
When a brother dies
it's like losing an arm.

19:32.421 --> 19:34.582
Be strong, masino.

19:47.937 --> 19:50.553
Totuccio was saved by a miracle

19:50.606 --> 19:55.350
and now he wants to slaughter
the corleonesi with his bare hands.

19:55.861 --> 19:57.977
But what can he do alone?

19:58.739 --> 20:01.230
He hasn't got this.

20:02.576 --> 20:05.192
But you've got this.

20:10.876 --> 20:12.992
Tano, what do you want?

20:17.717 --> 20:20.254
All the heroin in the world
passes through palermo,

20:20.344 --> 20:22.881
there's billions for everyone.

20:23.264 --> 20:28.099
And the corleonesi are wiping out
half the world, women, kids...

20:29.729 --> 20:31.344
You know what scarpuzzedda did?

20:32.898 --> 20:34.980
To Toto inzerillo's son?

20:35.276 --> 20:39.144
First he cut off his arm,
then he killed him.

20:40.531 --> 20:42.396
What need was there?

20:43.159 --> 20:44.774
You're not even safe here.

20:45.786 --> 20:48.027
Stefano wanted to stop riina,

20:48.122 --> 20:51.364
he spoke to the commission about it,
he wanted to shoot him.

20:53.419 --> 20:55.034
Why didn't they do it?

20:55.296 --> 20:59.005
They would have, but riina is smart
and he didn't go to the meeting.

21:00.676 --> 21:02.416
Who's still on our side?

21:03.554 --> 21:05.670
We're losing many
of them along the way,

21:05.806 --> 21:09.014
they've gone over
to those louts of riina's.

21:09.059 --> 21:11.015
But we're not dead yet,

21:11.061 --> 21:14.053
we're not dead, we can still make it.

21:18.194 --> 21:19.900
But you gotta come back.

21:21.697 --> 21:23.312
You get me?

21:25.326 --> 21:28.159
The salvos told me too,
ignazio asked me.

21:32.583 --> 21:34.448
Besides, we're not alone in Rome,

21:34.585 --> 21:36.701
there's still our friends.

21:37.713 --> 21:40.329
- What does pippo say?
- Mr calo?

21:42.218 --> 21:46.086
He's in Rome, he says
he's working for his career.

21:49.475 --> 21:53.434
I'm not scared of dying,
I'm not scared of anything,

21:54.355 --> 21:56.937
but to go there and tell them:

21:58.359 --> 22:00.350
"Here I am, kill me"... why?

22:01.987 --> 22:03.102
For glory?

22:04.240 --> 22:06.982
Like the kamikazes?

22:09.745 --> 22:11.235
Am I a jerk?

22:12.498 --> 22:16.366
We gotta kill them,
before they kill us.

22:18.629 --> 22:20.995
We need to think it through, tano.

23:05.801 --> 23:07.541
- Hello?
- It's me.

23:08.304 --> 23:10.044
Can you hear me?

23:11.432 --> 23:13.297
I can't hear you very well.

23:14.310 --> 23:17.052
- Benedetto and Antonio...
- Are you crying?

23:19.648 --> 23:23.266
- Benedetto and Antonio are gone.
- Put my wife on.

23:26.322 --> 23:28.438
Hello? Masino, I'm here.

23:31.452 --> 23:34.535
What's going on?
Did you call Cal?

23:34.955 --> 23:37.196
Of course, but he never answers.

23:38.417 --> 23:40.578
Masino, you gotta
come here immediately.

23:41.587 --> 23:46.081
They're our sons, your sons!
They've gone, don't you see?

23:46.216 --> 23:48.207
What do you mean
he never answers?

23:50.179 --> 23:51.965
You gotta come here!

23:52.056 --> 23:53.592
I'll take care of it now.

23:53.724 --> 23:55.589
I'll take care of it now!

25:44.209 --> 25:46.325
Why aren't you in bed?

25:46.837 --> 25:48.702
I was waiting for you.

25:57.598 --> 25:59.463
What's going on?

26:02.936 --> 26:04.426
Nothing.

26:05.064 --> 26:06.600
Nothing.

26:28.253 --> 26:29.584
Stay here!

26:37.513 --> 26:39.253
Stay calm.

26:40.516 --> 26:43.633
I'm putting it down, stay calm.

26:56.657 --> 26:58.397
Stay calm.

27:11.672 --> 27:15.915
Mr tommaso "buskettaâ€
we have a warrant for your arrest

27:16.009 --> 27:18.500
and to search your house.

27:18.804 --> 27:21.921
- His name is Roberto felici.
- Start with his office.

27:22.057 --> 27:24.924
Then the bedrooms,
I want to find the drugs.

27:25.018 --> 27:27.304
There are no drugs here.

27:28.689 --> 27:30.554
So where's the money, then?

27:30.941 --> 27:33.148
If you collaborate
things will be much easier.

27:33.694 --> 27:36.436
Here's his passport,
his name's Roberto felici.

27:36.572 --> 27:39.063
You're in the wrong house.
For the love of god...

27:39.158 --> 27:41.194
Enough! Shut up!

27:42.786 --> 27:44.151
Shut up!

27:47.583 --> 27:49.323
- Mr "busketta"...
- Buscetta.

27:50.794 --> 27:53.831
My name is tommaso buscetta,
you need to say it properly.

27:53.964 --> 27:55.420
Cuff him.

27:55.465 --> 27:56.955
Let's start the search.

27:58.343 --> 27:59.343
Please.

28:36.506 --> 28:38.622
Who did you traffic heroin with? Speak!

28:55.859 --> 28:58.145
Who's your contact?

28:59.029 --> 29:01.145
Speak, you filthy trafficker!

29:59.548 --> 30:05.339
July 7, 1984 Rio de Janeiro,
talavera Bruce prison

30:28.952 --> 30:30.943
Italy's beautiful, isn't it?

30:31.997 --> 30:33.112
Yes.

30:34.333 --> 30:36.745
But I'm not going there on vacation.

30:38.587 --> 30:39.997
I know all of Italy,

30:40.130 --> 30:43.998
or rather all the prisons of Italy.

30:46.970 --> 30:48.380
Want a cigarette?

30:50.974 --> 30:52.259
Thanks.

31:05.489 --> 31:07.480
How far to the airport?

31:10.243 --> 31:13.656
First we have to stop by the hospital
to get you checked out,

31:13.747 --> 31:18.241
the government wants to ensure
they send you to Italy in good health.

31:19.503 --> 31:22.666
They want to show that
you have been treated well in Brazil.

31:28.178 --> 31:29.543
What's happening to him?

31:29.638 --> 31:31.674
Hold his head!

31:33.266 --> 31:35.678
Go faster!

31:35.769 --> 31:37.805
Faster to the hospital.

31:38.563 --> 31:44.058
- Did he poison himself?
- He's having convulsions! Go faster!

31:47.948 --> 31:52.942
Go faster, before he dies on us here.

32:22.858 --> 32:24.348
Darling.

32:30.949 --> 32:32.735
You're safe.

32:48.467 --> 32:53.131
July 14, 1984
Rio de Janeiro, extradition to Italy

33:37.807 --> 33:39.547
You all right?

35:28.293 --> 35:29.533
Doctor?

35:32.172 --> 35:33.878
What's wrong?

35:38.928 --> 35:40.168
Breathe.

35:40.805 --> 35:42.545
Breathe, come on.

35:55.445 --> 35:56.901
That's it.

35:58.698 --> 36:00.404
Breathe, slowly.

36:18.176 --> 36:20.087
- De gennaro?
- Yes?

36:22.097 --> 36:25.589
- Where are you taking me?
- Judge Falcone will explain it to you.

36:26.476 --> 36:28.967
- I'm not talking to anyone.
- All right.

36:29.688 --> 36:31.804
Rest now, just relax.

37:07.392 --> 37:08.723
You're not eating?

37:10.979 --> 37:12.515
I'm not hungry, thank you.

37:28.163 --> 37:30.370
No, it's not necessary.

37:46.681 --> 37:49.172
July 15, 1984
Rome, fiumicino airport

37:49.559 --> 37:52.301
tommaso buscetta, 56,
known as Don masino

37:52.395 --> 37:57.059
has returned to his homeland in
handcuffs, hidden under a blanket.

37:57.650 --> 37:59.686
A week ago,
the head of the sicilian mafia

37:59.819 --> 38:02.777
tried to kill himself in Brazil
with strychnine,

38:02.947 --> 38:05.529
but it didn't help him
avoid extradition.

38:06.409 --> 38:10.197
His presence had become awkward
for the Brazilian authorities.

38:10.413 --> 38:12.404
In south America, Don masino

38:12.582 --> 38:15.699
had created a fortune
starting in the '60s.

38:16.461 --> 38:20.170
He was first been extradited
from Brazil in 1972,

38:20.215 --> 38:23.082
incarcerated first
at the ucciardone, then in turin,

38:23.176 --> 38:26.088
following a conviction
for drug trafficking,

38:26.179 --> 38:30.843
buscetta managed to escape
from turin in 1980,

38:30.975 --> 38:33.557
where he had obtained semi-Liberty

38:33.603 --> 38:35.594
and took refuge in Brazil.

38:36.064 --> 38:38.976
Linked to the badalamentis
and other families

38:39.108 --> 38:41.064
of the so-called
"failing" palermo mafia...

38:41.361 --> 38:46.481
July 16, 1984 Rome,
San vitale police headquarters

38:49.077 --> 38:50.567
wait here.

39:05.635 --> 39:08.627
I'd like you to meet mr pajno,
the prosecutor of palermo,

39:08.721 --> 39:11.212
and judge Giovanni Falcone.

39:13.142 --> 39:16.009
I wanted to reassure you personally

39:16.396 --> 39:20.639
that your family has full protection
in the United States.

39:22.026 --> 39:24.642
Also, at the judiciary committee

39:25.029 --> 39:28.146
a law is being considered,
also in Italy, to offer

39:28.408 --> 39:32.993
material guarantees and personal
safety to state informants.

39:33.288 --> 39:34.903
I am not an informant.

39:34.998 --> 39:36.909
Yes, of course.

39:37.292 --> 39:39.658
You're free to make
all the statements you want.

39:41.129 --> 39:44.417
I only wanted to inform you
that the state is not inert.

39:45.383 --> 39:48.045
Good, then I'll leave you
to judge Falcone.

39:48.887 --> 39:50.297
All the best with it.

40:00.189 --> 40:02.555
So, first name and last name.

40:07.697 --> 40:09.938
Buscetta tommaso.

40:12.577 --> 40:15.193
The late benedetto
and the late bauccio Felicia,

40:16.289 --> 40:19.326
born in palermo July 13, 1928,

40:20.168 --> 40:23.080
elementary school, no military service,

40:23.713 --> 40:26.580
married with children,
agricultural businessman.

40:28.301 --> 40:30.917
- Previously convicted.
- It's the law...

40:31.095 --> 40:32.210
Yes, yes.

40:38.978 --> 40:41.310
Good. Shall we start?

40:43.191 --> 40:45.102
I'm not an informant.

40:46.361 --> 40:47.942
Changed your mind?

40:48.738 --> 40:51.980
I confess I'm surprised, I thought
you wanted to collaborate,

40:52.116 --> 40:53.731
that's why we came here.

40:54.994 --> 40:58.111
I'm not a spy, a rat...

41:00.083 --> 41:02.699
I have been a man of honor
and I'm ready

41:02.752 --> 41:04.834
to pay my debt with the law.

41:07.215 --> 41:08.250
Now then...

41:13.596 --> 41:16.588
There's one question
I will not answer.

41:17.475 --> 41:20.262
Actually, I'll answer it
before you ask me.

41:20.979 --> 41:23.265
I have never trafficked drugs.

41:24.023 --> 41:25.854
It's pointless asking me.

41:32.240 --> 41:33.776
How much do you smoke?

41:38.413 --> 41:39.528
- None left?
- No.

41:40.540 --> 41:42.280
Take mine.

41:49.257 --> 41:50.667
Right...

41:52.301 --> 41:54.917
Shall we start with your affiliation?

41:56.639 --> 41:58.800
To give the questioning an order.

42:06.065 --> 42:07.646
I'm tired.

42:12.447 --> 42:13.562
Good.

42:17.410 --> 42:20.402
Read and sign here.

42:26.586 --> 42:29.544
- The packet.
- Keep it, I have another one.

43:16.094 --> 43:18.631
- Good day, then.
- And to you.

43:19.263 --> 43:21.879
- If you need anything, send for me.
- Thank you.

43:24.977 --> 43:28.265
- Never leave him by himself.
- Do I leave the door open?

43:33.736 --> 43:36.478
Would you like me to turn on the TV?

43:37.406 --> 43:39.738
That's not necessary, thank you.

43:40.535 --> 43:43.902
- Have any preference for lunch?
- I'm not hungry.

43:46.290 --> 43:49.157
- Something light.
- All right.

44:47.727 --> 44:49.092
Mama.

44:52.440 --> 44:54.226
What's happening?

45:01.991 --> 45:05.233
Masino, what have you done?

45:07.872 --> 45:09.487
How could you leave me?

45:09.624 --> 45:12.991
My husband, what have you done?

45:13.586 --> 45:16.202
You left me with these kids...

45:17.506 --> 45:20.248
Masino, my husband.

45:20.885 --> 45:24.753
What a weight I feel in my chest!

45:34.357 --> 45:37.269
Our pillar is leaving us...

45:54.168 --> 45:56.784
My son, come with me.

45:57.672 --> 45:59.788
Come with me.

46:00.549 --> 46:04.041
My beautiful boy...

46:18.693 --> 46:20.183
What's going on?

46:21.445 --> 46:23.902
Judge Falcone will do
the next interrogation in here.

46:25.032 --> 46:26.397
Why?

46:26.826 --> 46:29.283
Mr de gennaro ordered it
for your safety.

46:37.420 --> 46:40.036
There's a phone call for you
from your wife.

46:53.602 --> 46:55.217
Turn them on, please.

46:56.480 --> 46:57.811
